verbs.description: The special counsel Robert Mueller [V: has] issued two subpoenas to a social media expert who worked for longtime Donald Trump adviser Roger Stone during the 2016 presidential election campaign . The subpoenas were delivered late last week to lawyers representing Jason Sullivan .
